    "summary": "Buffer exposes a public GraphQL API at https://api.buffer.com, an npm CLI (`buffer`), and an integrations/docs portal; API access requires either a personal API key or an OAuth client, while the CLI uses the same API key via `buffer init` or `BUFFER_API_KEY`.",
