        "type": "api_key",
        "label": "Buffer API Key",
        "generateUrl": "https://publish.buffer.com/settings/api",
        "setup": "Go to [Settings → API](https://publish.buffer.com/settings/api) in your Buffer account, open the **Personal Keys** tab, click **+ New Key**, name it, choose scopes, set an expiration, and generate the key. The docs say email verification is required and only organization owners can create keys. Copy the token and store it as `BUFFER_API_KEY` or paste it into tools that ask for a bearer token.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
      "buffer_oauth_client": {
        "type": "oauth2",
        "label": "Buffer OAuth client",
        "generateUrl": "https://publish.buffer.com/settings/api",
        "setup": "Register an app in [Settings → API](https://publish.buffer.com/settings/api). Buffer supports OAuth 2.0 with Authorization Code + PKCE. Confidential clients receive a `client_id` and `client_secret`; public clients receive only a `client_id` and use PKCE. Bring your own redirect URI that exactly matches what you register.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
      },
