        "label": "Buffer CLI login token",
        "generateUrl": "https://publish.buffer.com/settings/api",
        "setup": "Install the CLI, then run `buffer init` to save your API token, default organization, and timezone into the global config. If you do not want to persist a token, set `BUFFER_API_KEY` in your shell and skip `buffer init`. The CLI can also install Buffer skills into Claude Code or Codex.",
        "acquisition": "manual"
